Version 0.20.16
16 July 2014

 - Fixed encoding issue in album search feature
 - Fix downloading issue with FAT32 filesystem (#61)
 - Fix mplayer doesn't remember last volume (#44)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.20.14
May 7 2014

 - Added album search feature (vixus0)
    (enter "album" optionally followed by album name to search)
 - Remove decimal point from size in results when not needed
 - Fix progress bar size exceeds terminal width
 - Added cache to persistent storage for http search requests
    cached items expire after 3 days
    use "clearcache" command to force clear cache

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

